The paper focuses on imitation learning for robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of probabilistic approaches and variance estimation suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the approach to a painting task involves computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY).
